*-- Documentation (optional):
Display Mode controls how the notification is shown to users:

BANNER (Default):
- Fixed banner at top of screen
- Remains visible until user closes it
- Best for: Critical messages requiring acknowledgment

TOAST:
- Bottom-right corner notification
- Auto-dismisses after 5 seconds
- Best for: Non-intrusive updates, confirmations

BOTH:
- Shows both banner and toast simultaneously
- Maximum visibility for important messages
- Best for: Critical announcements needing immediate attention

SILENT:
- No UI display, logged only
- Accessible via /log REST endpoint
- Best for: Audit trail, compliance, background monitoring

Default: BANNER (for backward compatibility with v1.0.0)
